COMMANDS LIST:
1. # - comment line, ignored
2. PUSH value : place value on top of the stack
3. POP value : remove value from top of the stack
4. +, -, *, / : sum, dif, mul, div operators
    POP v1, v2; apply the operator; PUSH result
5. SQRT value : square root operator
    POP value; calculate square root; PUSH result
6. PRINT : print top value in the stack
7. DEFINE alias value : set an alias (alphabetic) for a value
8. EXIT : exit calculator
